1. As a user, I should be able to select the degree of difficulty I want the trivia quiz to be:
New to Game of Thrones [Easy  difficulty questions ], 
Regular fan of Game of Thrones [Medium  difficulty questions ], 
Die-Hard Fan of Game of Thrones [Expert difficulty questions ].

2. As a user, I should be able to select one of four multiple choice answer options to answer the question.

3. As a user, I should be able to request a hint that will provide me a phrase that will assist me in answering the question at hand.

4. As a user, I should be able to see the results of my submission once the trivia	quiz is complete.

5. As a user, I should be able to send my results to myself via email.
